+# ADR 0000: Decision title
+
+- Status: Proposed
+- Date: YYYY-MM-DD
+- Owners: role or maintainer
+
+## Context
+
+What forces the decision? What evidence and constraints matter?
+
+## Decision
+
+What will be done, precisely?
+
+## Alternatives considered
+
+What credible alternatives were rejected, and why?
+
+## Consequences
+
+Positive, negative, migration, operational, and security consequences.
+
+## Validation and rollback
+
+How will the decision be tested, and how can it be reversed or superseded?
